flowchart LR
    A[React dashboard sends compliance request] --> B[Backend API receives request]
    B --> C[ComplianceController validates input]
    C --> D[OAuthService gets provider token]
    D --> E[Resolve mapped tools and logic]
    E --> F[Collect evidence with ToolExecutionStrategy]
    F --> G{ToolResolver selects mode}

    G -. decision logic .-> GX[Use MCP when tool is exposed and supported then apply preference then fallback to REST]

    G -->|MCP| H[Backend McpClient]
    H --> H1[Select provider MCP URL from env]
    H1 --> H2[Post JSON RPC tools call]
    H2 --> H3{Provider}
    H3 -->|github| H4[GitHub MCP server]
    H3 -->|gitlab| H5[GitLab MCP server]
    H3 -->|bitbucket| H6[Bitbucket MCP server]
    H4 --> J[Normalize evidence payload]
    H5 --> J
    H6 --> J

    G -->|REST fallback| I[REST fallback client calls provider REST API]
    I --> J

    J --> K[EvaluationEngine evaluates evidence]
    K --> L[ReportFormatter builds summary and table]
    L --> M[Backend returns compliance report JSON]